ash Free Dog Run\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/leash-free-dog-run\",\"description\":\"Leash Free Dog Run is a favorite spot for dog owners in Kansas City.\\n\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play, climate-controlled areas, professional...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Kansas City\",\"addressRegion\":\"MO\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":6,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/river-market-dog-park\",\"name\":\"River Market Dog Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/river-market-dog-park\",\"description\":\"If you're in Kansas City, bring your furry friend to River Market Dog Park for a great day out.\\n\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather play,...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Kansas City\",\"addressRegion\":\"MO\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":7,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dcid-walnut-st-dog-park\",\"name\":\"DCID Walnut St. Dog Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/dcid-walnut-st-dog-park\",\"description\":\"Located in Kansas City, DCID Walnut St. Dog Park offers a welcoming space for pets to exercise and socialize.\\n\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for all-weather...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Kansas City\",\"addressRegion\":\"MO\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":8,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/west-terrace-dog-park-private-membership-based-park\",\"name\":\"West Terrace Dog Park (private, membership-based park)\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/west-terrace-dog-park-private-membership-based-park\",\"description\":\"West Terrace Dog Park (private, membership-based park) provides a safe and fun environment for dogs of all sizes in the heart of Kansas City.\\n\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Kansas City\",\"addressRegion\":\"MO\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}3:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$c\"}}]\nd:T46f,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I walk my dog in Kansas City, KS?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Wyandotte County Lake Park is a premier destination, offering ample hiking trails and beautiful lake views for leashed walks. It is a massive green space within the city.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there a dog park in Kansas City, KS?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"While KCK utilizes many shared metro resources, the nearby Shawnee Mission Park extends a massive off-leash area that is a short drive away and highly popular with KCK residents.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there dog-friendly breweries in KCK?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, several breweries in the area welcome dogs on their patios. It is a great way to relax after a hike at the lake.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in Wyandotte County?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Dogs must be leashed when in public parks and residential areas. Strict enforcement helps maintain safety in the citys busy parks.\"}}]}4:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$d\"}}]\n5:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Kansas City\\\"}]}\"}}]\n6:[\"$\",\"$Le\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"$Lf\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n15:T878,Located on the vibrant riverfront of Kansas City, Bar K is far more than just a typical dog park—it is a revolutionary community destination that completely reimagines the dog-friendly experience for modern pet owners. This expansive two-acre facility uniquely combines a professionally maintained, fully staffed dog park with a modern bar, restaurant, and event space, creating a one-of-a-kind environment where pups and people can socialize in style. The park features thoughtfully designed separate play areas for large and small dogs, all supervised by trained 'Dogtenders' who actively monitor play to ensure safe and fun interactions for every visitor. Customizable agility courses, climbing structures, and seasonal splash pools keep active dogs entertained for hours, while the climate-controlled indoor spaces provide year-round comfort, ensuring the fun never stops regardless of the unpredictable Missouri weather. Whether you are looking for a place to let your dog burn off excess energy or a spot to relax with a locally brewed craft beer while your furry friend plays nearby, Bar K offers an unparalleled experience that bridges the gap between a dog park and a social club.\n\nBeyond the impressive outdoor play areas, Bar K excels in hospitality, offering a robust experience for both humans and hounds. The on-site restaurant serves a diverse menu of healthy, locally sourced food for pet parents, alongside a dedicated 'Doggie Menu' featuring gourmet treats like beef stew, turkey meatballs, and dog-friendly ice cream. The facility serves as a vibrant hub for social events, regularly hosting adoption drives in partnership with local shelters, live music performances, and even trivia nights, fostering a tight-knit community of dog lovers. With a strong focus on safety, cleanliness, and member satisfaction, Bar K has established itself as a premier destination in the Midwest. Its innovative approach has set a new standard for dog parks across the country. For more information on [membership options](https://barkdogbar.com/) and day passes, or to find other top-rated local favorites, visit [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).16:T63a,Nestled within the historic and sprawling Swope Park, Swope Dog Park provides a fantastic five-acre off-leash haven for Kansas City's canine residents. This fully fenced facility is thoughtfully divided into two distinct sections: a spacious four-acre area for large dogs to romp and run, and a designated one-acre area for small dogs or those who prefer a gentler playstyle. The park's terrain is a mix of grassy fields and shaded wooded areas, offering plenty of variety for exploration. A crushed limestone loop trail circles the main area, providing a perfect path for owners to walk while keeping an eye on their pets as they socialize and play.\n\nSwope Dog Park is equipped with excellent amenities to ensure a comfortable visit, including drinking fountains for both people and pets, benches for relaxation, and waste stations to keep the area clean. The large mature trees provide ample shade during the warmer months, making it a pleasant destination year-round. Its location within Swope Park—often called the jewel of the Kansas City park system—means you are just steps away from other major attractions like the Kansas City Zoo and Starlight Theatre, allowing you to easily plan a full day of fun. Whether you are a local regular or just passing through, this park offers a safe and welcoming environment for dogs of all sizes. Visit the [official Swope Park page](https://kcparks.org/places/swope-park-off-leash-park/) for current hours and maintenance schedules. For more information on the best dog parks in the metro, visit [Indoor Dog Park](https://www.indoordogpark.org/).8:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Kansas City\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park In Kansas City\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Explore Wyandotte County Lake and nearby dog parks in Kansas City, KS. A guide to pet-friendly living in KCK.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Kansas City, Kansas (KCK), offers vast green spaces and easy access to the entire metro's pet amenities. Wyandotte County Lake Park is a standout feature, providing miles of trails and water views for leashed adventures. While KCK residents often utilize destination dog parks in neighboring suburbs like Shawnee Mission, the local community is filled with dog lovers. Indoor options are primarily found in private daycare centers that offer climate-controlled play.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"The city's diverse neighborhoods offer plenty of sidewalks for daily exercise. The proximity to downtown KC means that world-class facilities like Bar K are just a short drive away. KCK provides a more relaxed, nature-oriented pace of life while keeping big-city amenities within reach. It is an ideal spot for dog owners who want large yards and access to massive county parks.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/kansas-city/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Kansas City dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"city\":\"Kansas City\",\"state\":\"MO\"}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"className\":\"city-insights-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L14\",null,{\"parks\":[{\"id\":\"ChIJmf-d103xwIcR4snbOIUtk9w\",\"name\":\"Bar K\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$15\",\"slug\":\"bar-k\",\"address\":\"501 Berkley Pkwy\",\"street\":\"501 Berkley Pkwy\",\"city\":\"Kansas City\",\"state\":\"MO\",\"zipCode\":\"64120\",\"full_address\":\"501 Berkley Pkwy, Kansas City, MO 64120, USA\",\"latitude\":39.1146958,\"longitude\":-94.5778314,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJmf-d103xwIcR4snbOIUtk9w\",\"phone\":\"(816) 474-2275\",\"website\":\"http://www.barkdogbar.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":3328,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"12:00 – 9:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\